    %% Connections
    UI --> WSClient & RESTClient
    WSClient -->|"WebSocket /ws/agent"| WSHandler
    RESTClient -->|"HTTP"| REST
    REST --> Handlers
    WSHandler --> SessionInbox
    SessionInbox --> OrcApi
    Handlers --> OrcApi

    OrcApi --> PipelineRunner
    PipelineRunner --> FSM & RunSM
    PipelineRunner --> SessionLane
    FSM --> HeadAgent
    HeadAgent --> Planner & ToolSelector & Synthesizer
    HeadAgent --> CoreAgents & SpecialistAgents & IndustryAgents
    HeadAgent -->|spawnt Subrun| SubrunLane
    SubrunLane -->|on_subrun_completed| CoordBridge
    CoordBridge --> ConfRouter
    ConfRouter -->|confidence_decision| HeadAgent
    CoordBridge -->|write| Blackboard
    Blackboard -->|watcher notify| CoordBridge
    CoordBridge -->|report_result| Supervisor
    Supervisor -->|confidence OK| MsgBus
    Supervisor -->|confidence low: redelegate| SubrunLane
    Supervisor -->|write audit| Blackboard
    CoordBridge --> AgentReg
    MsgBus --> ParExec & Consensus

    HeadAgent --> ModelRouter
    ModelRouter --> ModelRegistry & HealthTracker & CtxGuard
    ModelRouter --> LlmClient
    LlmClient --> Ollama & OpenAI

    HeadAgent --> MemStore & LTM
    SQLiteState --> LTM
    PipelineRunner --> SQLiteState

    HeadAgent --> ToolPolicy
    ToolPolicy --> PolicyApproval
    PolicyApproval --> CircuitBreaker
    AgentIso --> ToolPolicy

    HeadAgent --> SkillsSvc
    SkillsSvc --> Discovery
    McpBridge --> ToolExecMgr

    HeadAgent --> Reflection & Verification & ActionParser
    HeadAgent --> PromptKernel & ToolExecMgr & LearningLoop
    ToolExecMgr --> ToolTelemetry & SelfHealing

